dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Wayne Hayes. May I have your name, please?
Hello, Wayne. My name is Jane Robinson.
Nice to meet you, Jane. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six three two one and I was born on the twentieth of May, nineteen eighty-eight.
Thank you, Jane. One more thing, could you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle?
Of course, it's a two zero one five Toyota Camry.
Thank you for providing the details, Jane. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Wayne.
You're welcome, Jane. Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day.
